      "content": "Thanks, this is a good start. Could you add a sentence specifically mentioning that their tardiness is affecting the morning warehouse handover process? We really need everyone there on time to get the trucks loaded. Also, can you make it sound a little less \"robotic\"? Just a bit more human, but still strictly professional.",
